K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-13: de yi drung du dgod par bshad //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-14: mkha' lding rnam par 'dud pa'i bu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-15: mthu rtsal shin tu rdzogs pa'ang gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-16: de nas 'byung po'i tshogs rnams dgod //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-17: chu lha yang ni nub phyogs gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-18: gsum pa dag kyang 'das pa yi; ;bzhi pa dag gis bshad par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-19: bang rim bzhi pa'i steng dag tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-20: rdo rje shugs kyis song nas ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-21: nyi ma rnams ni g-yog dang bcas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-22: chu lha'i phyogs su gnas par bya; ;bden bral phyogs su srin rnams dgod //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-23: de yi pha rol grul bum gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-24: de nas grul bum lcags can yang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-25: lho phyogs su ni gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-26: me yi phyogs su rlung lha gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-27: shar phyogs zla ba 'khor dang bcas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-28: thag bzang ris kyang de bzhin te //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-29: de gnyis kyis ni bzhi pa dgang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:219b-30: de nas bang rim ldan pa la //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-2: lha bsrung phyir ni klu rnams kyang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-3: chu lha'i phyogs su dgod par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-4: dbang ldan dang ni shar mtshams su //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-5: lha yi mdzod kyang gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-6: gzhan gyis mi thub rdo rje che //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-7: dbang ldan phyogs su gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-8: de nas rdo rje'i drung dag tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-9: gnas gtsang rigs kyi lha chen gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-10: lha yi srung ma gnod sbyin che //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-11: byang phyogs dag tu gnas par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-12: rdo rje shugs kyis drug pa la //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-13: song nas chu lha'i phyogs dag tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-14: klu rgyal rgya mtsho chen po'i bu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-15: drag cing shugs dang ldan pa gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-16: der ni g-yog dang bcas par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-17: gzhan dag gis ni sprul pa la //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-18: dbang byed la ni gang yin rnams //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-19: bden bral phyogs su gnas par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-20: tshangs ris kyi ni tshogs rnams kyang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-21: me yi phyogs su dgod par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-22: tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-23: lha rnams shar phyogs gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-24: shin tu mthong lha dbang ldan du //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-25: srid rtse de yi pha rol dgod //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-26: de bzhin dka' zlog byang phyogs gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-27: drug pa dag kyang 'das pa yin //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-28: bang rim dag ni bdun pa la //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-29: rdo rje shugs kyis rdo rje 'chang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-30: song nas klu yi gtso po ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-31: rgya mtsho chen po rmad byung gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220a-32: byang phyogs bya ba zin nas ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-0: grags shing @220b bsod nams che ba yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-1: 'phrul dga' ba yi lha chen rnams //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-2: gshin rje'i phyogs su gnas par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-3: de nas rdo rje shar phyogs kyi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-4: gnas kyi gtso bor gzhag par bya; ;sum cu gsum pa'ang shar phyogs su //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-5: gzhag cing bdun pa yongs su dgang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-6: lha rnams sna tshogs rgyas pa yis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-7: ri yi dbang po dam pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-8: bang rim dag ni yongs su rdzogs //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-9: de yi 'og tu bya ba bshad //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-10: ri rab steng du thams cad mkhyen //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-11: rig sngags snying po 'chang ba po //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-12: sangs rgyas 'jig rten rtogs mdzad pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-13: thar pa'i grong khyer dbang phyug gzhan //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-14: gang gi 'od zer de dag gis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-15: phyogs rnams thams cad rgyas mdzad dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-16: gang gis sku la mtshan kun gyi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-17: mdzod rnams thams cad 'byung ba dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-18: mtshan dang gzhon dang brtson 'grus dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-19: gzhan yang zhi bar ldan pa dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-20: mchog rnams mchog sbyin byed pa la //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-21: gang gis mchog gi mchog sbyin dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-22: thugs rje che dang ldan pa'i mgon //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-24: 'od zer nyi ma bye ba yis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-25: gang gis mun pa bsal ba dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-26: chos dang mtshan nyid rig pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-27: yid bzhin nor bu'i thugs mnga' gang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-28: gang gis bskal pa grangs med par //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-29: sems can rnams ni rab tu bsrungs //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:220b-30: rin chen sindra n'i la ltar //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-2: nor bu yi ni rgyal po bzhin //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-3: zla mdog can gyi mdzod srung na //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-4: gang gi bdud rtsi gtor ba'i zhal //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-6: dus mtshams gser gyis bsgyur ba yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-7: gser gyi ri ltar sku mdog mdzes //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-8: 'khor lo chen po rtsibs stong pas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-9: phyag dang zhabs ni legs spras pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-10: skyil mo krung ni mdzes pa yis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-11: thub pa chen po legs par bzhugs //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-12: chos kyi chu klung chen po'i mchog /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-13: de yi zhal nas kun tu 'bab //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-14: rmad du byung bar 'bab pa ste //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-15: bdag gis kha ni stong phrag rnams //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-16: stong snyed kyis ni brjod pa 'am //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-17: khong du chud par nus mi 'gyur //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-18: de ni rgyas par 'gengs pa dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-19: ye shes pha mtha' bla na med //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-20: shin tu rmad byung gsang bar bshad //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-21: tshig ldan gyi ni lha mo de //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-22: 'jig rten mgon po sangs rgyas kyi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-23: gsung la rab tu gnas pa yin //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-24: 'jig rten gsum na bdag mchog sbyin //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-25: 'jig rten gsum gyis phyag byas pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-28: che ba'i che mchog stobs chen te //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-29: dga' zhing kun gyi tshig la gnas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-30: gzhan gcig sangs rgyas 'dra bar med //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-31: gud na yang ni gnas ma yin //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221a-32: de yi bsngags pa sangs rgyas sam //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-0: lha rnams @221b nyid kyis brjod par nus //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-1: mchog sbyin 'jig rten gsum gyi ma //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-2: nyes pa thams cad rnam par spangs //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-4: khyod kyi rang bzhin nyid yin te //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-5: lha dang dri za klu dbang dbang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-6: gnod sbyin lha min tshogs bskor ba'i //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-7: rgyu dang mi rgyu rnams kyi gter //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-8: ya mtshan las kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-9: der gtogs der ni brtson zhing spro //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-10: de dang 'brel bar the tshom med //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-11: chos klung bsod nams ldan pa de //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-12: bsod nams rin chen dag gis rgyas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-13: lag na rdo rje'i bsod nams kyis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-14: las kyi rgya mtsho dag las 'byung //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-15: chu klung rgya mtshor 'bab pa na //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-17: de bzhin chos kyi chu klung 'di //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-18: 'di dag gis bsten byas nas kyang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-19: lag na rdo rje'i mgo bo dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-20: rna gnyis dang ni gsum du dbab //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-21: zer ma 'phros pas lha mo dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-22: dbang phyug tshogs bcas phog par 'gyur //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-23: de phyir chos kyi chu klung 'di //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-24: sangs rgyas las ni 'byung byas la //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-25: lag na rdo rje'i mgo bor yang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-26: rab tu dbab cing bdug par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-27: bsod nams ldan pa'i chu klung rgya chen de nyid las //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-28: skye bo mtha' dag gcig tu sems btud nyan par byed //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-29: de nyid la ni lha rnams thams cad mngon par dga'//
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:221b-30: de nyid la ni rig sngags grub pa'i tshogs kun brten //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-2: rdo rje 'dzin pa nga yi dgongs pa bzhin du rdzogs //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-3: de nas dam tshig mkhyen pas dkyil 'khor rgyal po yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-4: gsang ba gang dang gang gsungs dga' rgyas bdag gis bshad //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-5: lag na rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor chen po dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rgyal po las /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-7: ri rab kyi ni byang phyogs su //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-8: chos kyi klung chen 'dzin pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-9: rdo rje 'dzin chen rab gtum pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-10: stobs chen lag na rdo rje gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-11: de yi rkang pa g-yon pa yis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-12: dbang phyug chen po mnan par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-13: g-yas pa yi ni rkang pa yis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-14: lha mo dka' zlog mnan par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-15: ri yi dbang po 'khor yug dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-16: bang rim dag gi bar dag tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-17: gling chen rnam pa bzhi po dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-18: gnas rnams ji bzhin gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-19: de nas chu klung bdun yang gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-20: lho phyogs su ni dbyibs legs pa'i //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-21: 'dzam bu gling ni gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-22: chu klung dang ni shing dang yul //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-23: sna tshogs kyis ni shin tu rgyas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-24: de yi mngon mtshan chen po ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-25: 'dzam bu'i shing mchog skyes pa de //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-26: 'phang du dpag tshad brgya yod do //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-27: 'og logs su ni gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-28: de nas chu klung bdun yang gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-29: nags tshal yang ni bdun dag dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222a-30: yid du 'ong ba'i ri bdun dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-0: @222b yul bdun dag kyang gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-1: dang po byang nas brtsam bya zhing //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-2: lho phyogs logs su thur du drang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-3: shar nas nub tu drang bya zhing //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-4: kho ra khor yug bsgrubs nas ni; ;rgyal ba'i gsung rab yid 'ong ba //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-5: chos kyi 'khor lo rjes sgrub pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-7: snying rje'i bdag nyid padma'i mchog /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-8: dge slong dge slong ma rnams dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-9: rgyal po dag gis bsten pa gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-10: 'dzam bu gling gi lho phyogs su //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-11: 'khri shing dag kyang bri bar bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-12: nub phyogs su ni ba lang spyod //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-13: chu bo brgyas ni gang ba dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-14: yul dang skye bo stong dag dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-15: ba lang khyu ni stong gis rgyas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-16: de bzhin shar gyi lus 'phags kyang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-17: shar phyogs su ni gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-18: yul rnams su ni gzhag par bya; ;yul rnams dang ni ri dag gis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-19: kun tu rab tu rgyas par gnas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-20: de nas gnas brtan chos skyong ba //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-21: bcu gnyis dag dang lhan cig tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-22: sgra gcan 'dzin zhes grags pa ste; ;sangs rgyas sras ni mngon sum gnas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-23: gnod sbyin lha min lto 'phye rnams //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-24: nyin mtshan du ni der song nas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-25: dri dang phreng ba dpe med pas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-26: mchod pa byed cing phyag kyang 'tshal //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-27: de nas byang gi sgra mi snyan //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-28: lhun po yi ni byang phyogs gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-29: gtsang zhing gru bzhi lham pa ste //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:222b-30: chu klung dag gis rab tu brgyan //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-0: gang dag gi ni tshe yi @223a *//
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-1: tshad; ;chig stong tshang par brjod pa dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-2: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsungs pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-3: sems can ya mtshan de na gnas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-4: rgya mtsho'i sa ni bskor ba yi; ;ri yi dam pa ri rab la //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-5: phyogs kyi lha ni bzhi po rnams //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-6: kun nas nges par gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-7: karsha pa na brgyad dag gis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-8: dkyil 'khor dang por rdo rje bri //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-9: de yi gnas rnams de dag tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-10: gser gyi gdu bu dag kyang bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-11: sgo rnams re rer don grub pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-12: rgyu dang mi rgyu 'jig rten gsum //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-13: thub par nus pa gang yin pa'i //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-14: sgo srung gnyis kyang gzhag par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-15: de yang sngags dang ldan bya zhing //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-16: kun tu gzhal yas rgyas par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-17: rdo rje thog thog lho phyogs bri //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-18: rdo rje khu tshur byang phyogs gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-19: de nas der ni lha bshos rnams //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-20: rnam pa sna tshogs bkra ba dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-21: bla med rab mdzes rgyas par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-22: dri dang me tog phreng bas mchod //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-23: zhib de'i thu lu sna tshogs pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-24: sbrang rtsis byugs shing gzab pa dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-25: legs byas aa shva ka barti //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-26: de bzhin be reg nas khur dbul //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-27: ji tsam du ni rgyas pa phul //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-28: de tsam du ni 'grub par bshad //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-29: 'bras kyi po thug tshu la ka /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-30: thug pa sbyar thug sa mi ta //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-31: 'bras can tshod ma sna tshogs pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-32: kha dog sna tshogs sor lngar ldan //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223a-33: de la sogs pa gang 'dod pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-0: lo ma sna @223b tshogs skyon med pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-1: yang na kham phor gsar pa 'am //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-2: padma'i lo ma dag la gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-3: nas dang gro dang mon sran gre'u //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-4: s'a lu dang ni til 'bru rnams //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-5: snod gsar dag gi nang du gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-6: yang na gzhan du de bzhin gzhag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-7: hvags dang kha ras gang ba dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-8: btung ba bsil zhing zhim pa dag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-9: snod gsar dag gi nang dag tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-10: bzhag nas rab tu dbul bar bya //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-15: ta la'i lo ma bsil yab dbul //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-16: dri zhim pa yi dri kun gyis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-17: dkyil 'khor la ni mchod par bya //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-21: dri zhim thams cad sbyar bas mchod //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-22: aa ga ru dang du ru ka /

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-26: yang na nang du song nas ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-27: de ni byang phyogs kha blta zhing //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-28: lag na rdo rje tshul bzhin 'bod //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-29: shin tu bkra shis tshigs bcad dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-30: de bzhin bde legs rdzogs pa gdon //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-31: de nas der ni rig sngags ma //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-32: rdo rje lcags kyu rtse mo can //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-33: rdo rje'i rigs las byung ba yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:223b-34: rig sngags bstan pa gang yin pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-1: bar bya; ;de nas thog mar spyan drang pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-2: ri rab de yi rtse mor ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-4: chos kyi chu klung spyan drang ba //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-5: dam pa 'di ni brjod bar bya; ;bkra shis tshigs bcad brjod pa dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-6: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-7: 'dus pa chen po'i mdo dag dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-8: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi dag dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-10: ma nyams the tshom med pa dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-12: seng+ge'i sgra ni dpe med gdon //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-13: de nas rdo rje rigs kyi yum //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-14: rig sngags rdo rje lcags kyu bzlas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-15: de nas kyang ni rtse mo can //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-16: de nas rdo rje rigs skyes kyi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-17: rig sngags dag ni gang 'dod dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-18: snying po 'gro lding gtum po dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-19: de yi steng dang 'dod pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-20: rdo rje ma dang 'og pag can //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-21: lu gu rgyud dang gtum mo dang //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-27: gnyis pa rdo rje dril bu ma //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-28: gsum pa rdo rje nag mo dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-29: bzhi pa gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-30: lnga pa rdo rje rol pa dang /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-31: drug pa yang ni rgod bag can //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-32: bdun pa rdo rje shugs yin te //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-34: dgu pa rdo rje dbyug pa ste //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224a-35: de ni sna tshogs gzugs zhes grags //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-13: des na las su sgrub pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-14: rig sngags des ni grub par 'gyur //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-15: rig sngags gang la dga' ba des //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-16: dkyil 'khor du ni bzlas brjod bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-17: lag na rdo rjes bshad pa yi //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-18: rig sngags mang po de nyid ni //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-26: dkon mchog gsum la gtso bor 'dzin //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-30: bslab gzhi lnga ni sbyin par bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-31: ming 'di zhes ni bya ba bdag /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:224b-32: phyin chad nam 'tsho'i bar dag tu //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225a-2: rku dang brdzun du smra ba dang //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225a-7: byin gyis brlab kyi cho ga'ang bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225a-8: de nas der ni bum pa bdun //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225a-9: chu ni rab tu blugs nas kyang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225a-10: blo gros rdo rjes sngags pa des //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225a-11: bdud rtsi yis ni brjod pa yin //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-1: 'byung ba la sogs rnams kyi rgyas //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-2: khyod ni de nyid ltung bar byed //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-4: 'di la dpyad par bya ba med //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-5: rtag tu khyod kyis dam tshig srung //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-6: rtag tu dkyil 'khro mchod pa gyis //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-18: dam tshig nges par gnas par 'gyur //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-19: de nas rdo rje de blangs la //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-26: de nas grur ni lugs nas kyang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-27: khor yug las ni brgal bar bya //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-28: lag pa btang nas de la ni //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-29: dkyil 'khor thams cad bstan par bya; ;'khrul pa med par me tog gis //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-30: mdun bzhugs bde gshegs man chad dang //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-31: dkyil 'khor gang dang gang mthong ba //
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:225b-32: de dang de la bde bar mchod //

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:226b-2: tan dang ldan pa mchog tu gyur pa gang dang

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:226b-12: gzi brjid dang ldan pa'i dkyil 'khor dam pa 'di
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:226b-13: ni / dpal skyed cing mchog tu myur ba'i cho ga yin pas na /

K12D0746-2_H0691-2:227b-0: sha ya sne @227b tsam dha ni /
K12D0746-2_H0691-2:227b-9: ki ki ka la ka la /
